node.text: 10 months after a life threatening injury in Morocco I’m so excited to share my story! Here’s the trailer to our 6 piece documentary series created by @laynestratton and @wsl. From the trip of a lifetime, to the fear of losing life, and the road to recovery of returning to what makes me, me. Very thankful for everyone who has been apart of my team, this is just the beginning of what to come! node.text: This is Sal, my brother from another mother. He is black and I am white, we have different parents and are from different parts of the world but we both bleed blood and breathe the same air.
